  "text": "To produce an efficient Arabic OCR system, effective performance evaluation of current OCR systems is essential. Furthermore, evaluating OCR performance contributes to monitoring progress in OCR system development, analysing the effectiveness of OCR systems, identifying open areas and providing a scientific explanation for the performance of OCR systems [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
